(214, 2, '2013-03-30 23:42:18', '2013-03-30 23:42:18', '<h1 class="entry-title">Student Senate</h1>\r\n		\r\n				<div class="entry-content">\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-1988" title="SGA Senate Header" src="http://sga.umw.edu/files/2012/03/SGA-Senate-Header.jpg" alt="" width="917" height="340" /></p>\r\n<p>Student Senate is the Legislative Branch of the Student Government Association. The Senate can legislate on any issue concerning students. All motions go through one of ten Senate Committees: <em>Academic and Faculty Affairs</em>, <em>Buildings and Grounds</em>, <em>Constitutional Order</em>, <em>Dining Advisory</em>, <em>Election Rules and Procedures</em>, <em>Ethics and Conduct</em>, <em>Legislative and Administrative Affairs</em>, <em>Publicity</em>, <em>Telecommunications</em>, and <em>Environmental Sustainability </em>before it&#8217;s voted on the floor.</p>\r\n<p>Senators are chosen through elections at the beginning of each academic year through the residence halls and the student body at-large.</p>\r\n<p>The SGA Vice-President serves as President of Senate and its official spokesperson. The Vice-President of Senate is elected at the beginning of each academic year from among the current senators. The Parliamentarian and Secretary are appointed by the President of Senate.</p>\r\n<p>You are still able to join the Senate during the school year by collecting fifty signatures from people at the University of Mary Washington. After you&#8217;ve gained enough signatures, show up to a senate meeting and request to be admitted into the ranks of the Senate. It&#8217;s always a good idea to email the Senate President ahead of time to do this.</p>\r\n<p>President of Senate: Robert Belcourt</p>\r\n<p>Vice-President: Monique dela Cruz</p>\r\n<p>Parliamentarian: Stephanie Preston</p>\r\n<p>Secretary: Laila Ayub</p>\r\n<p>To learn more about Student Senate contact the the current President of Senate, Robert Belcourt at rbelcour@mail.umw.edu.</p>\r\n<p>To submit a motion for consideration feel free to <a href="https://docs.google.com/open?id=0B7h6P4oEiedARjRTdWxfZ3ZNY0U" target="_blank">download the motion sheet here</a> or fill out <a title="Online Motion Sheet" href="http://sga.umw.edu/onlinemotion/" target="_blank">this online form</a>. It&#8217;s your school, your voice, your SGA.</p>\r\n		</div>', 'Legislative', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'executive', '', '', '2013-04-16 20:26:13', '2013-04-16 20:26:13', '', 190, 'http://rosemary.umw.edu/~mdunlap/umwsga/wordpress/?page_id=214', 0, 'page', '', 0),
