(407, 1, '2013-04-06 14:47:17', '2013-04-06 14:47:17', '<h3><img alt="New Executive Cabinet" src="http://sga.umw.edu/files/2013/02/New-Executive-Cabinet.jpg" width="613" height="234" /></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #000000;"><strong>The Student Government Association is here to remind you that your voice matters. </strong></span></h3>\r\nThe SGA is your voice to the administration. We’re here to remind you that your voice matters more than ever. We are a forum where students bring their concerns about campus issues ranging from academics to safety. We address local, state, and national issues which affect students while organizing community events to foster school spirit, and work together to bond the community. <a title="Agenda &amp; Meeting Minutes" href="http://sga.umw.edu/agenda/" target="_blank">SGA Executive Cabinet</a> and Senate Meeting Minutes are updated regularly, please check back for new information. We are so committed to representing you that we even have a representative at every level of the administration… including the Board of Visitors.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '296-revision-5', '', '', '2013-04-06 14:47:17', '2013-04-06 14:47:17', '', 296, 'http://rosemary.umw.edu/~mdunlap/umwsga/wordpress/?p=407', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
