(461, 1, '2013-04-11 21:21:11', '2013-04-11 21:21:11', '<h1>The Administrative Review Process</h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nThe University of Mary Washington has recently hired a third-party consultant to look at our universities academic and non-academic programs. In addition to things like administrative expenses, non-academic programs consist of programs like student activities that are pivotal to student life.\r\n\r\nThe two students selected by the Student Government Association Executive Cabinet will serve as full committee members and will provide feedback on behalf of student body. This process will continue from February until the fall of 2013.\r\n\r\nThe deadline for applications is Sunday, February 3, 2013. After reviewing all applications, the SGA Executive Cabinet will contact selected applicants for interviews. At the conclusion of the process, Executive Cabinet will select two students whom they feel will serve the student body well and accurately convey student concerns to the committee. The work required for student committee members will include attending one, two-hour meeting every other week and being responsible for a significant amount of reading and preparation. The students selected to serve on the committee must be able to participate for the next two semesters and can gain academic credit for their service. (The form of academic credit remains to be determined.)\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, please contact the Student Government Association at sga@mail.umw.edu.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>At this time, the SGA is no longer accepting applications.</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>To find out more about SGA positions please visit </strong></span><a href="http://rosemary.umw.edu/~mdunlap/umwsga/wordpress/?page_id=354">Elections</a>.</h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>[vfb id=1]</h4>\r\n</div>', 'Open Positions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '206-revision-31', '', '', '2013-04-11 21:21:11', '2013-04-11 21:21:11', '', 206, 'http://rosemary.umw.edu/~mdunlap/umwsga/wordpress/?p=461', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
